{"audioUrl": "", "duration": 121.26, "paragraphs": [{"id": "p1", "sentences": [{"id": "p1s1", "text": "¡Hola! Mi nombre es Lucas.", "boundaries": [{"text": "¡Hola! ", "start": 0.0, "end": 1.44}, {"text": "Mi ", "start": 1.591, "end": 2.043}, {"text": "nombre ", "start": 2.101, "end": 2.415}, {"text": "es ", "start": 2.438, "end": 2.543}, {"text": "Lucas.", "start": 2.624, "end": 3.274}]}, {"id": "p1s2", "text": "Yo tengo veinticinco años.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Yo ", "start": 3.866, "end": 4.122}, {"text": "tengo ", "start": 4.191, "end": 4.389}, {"text": "veinticinco ", "start": 4.423, "end": 5.004}, {"text": "años.", "start": 5.062, "end": 5.654}]}, {"id": "p1s3", "text": "Soy brasileño y vivo en la ciudad de San Pablo.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Soy ", "start": 6.246, "end": 6.49}, {"text": "brasileño ", "start": 6.536, "end": 7.21}, {"text": "y ", "start": 7.268, "end": 7.303}, {"text": "vivo ", "start": 7.361, "end": 7.57}, {"text": "en ", "start": 7.593, "end": 7.639}, {"text": "la ", "start": 7.674, "end": 7.744}, {"text": "ciudad ", "start": 7.779, "end": 8.081}, {"text": "de ", "start": 8.104, "end": 8.185}, {"text": "San ", "start": 8.231, "end": 8.359}, {"text": "Pablo.", "start": 8.417, "end": 8.905}]}, {"id": "p1s4", "text": "Mi casa es chica, pero es muy linda y cómoda.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Mi ", "start": 9.497, "end": 9.636}, {"text": "casa ", "start": 9.683, "end": 9.973}, {"text": "es ", "start": 10.066, "end": 10.159}, {"text": "chica, ", "start": 10.228, "end": 10.623}, {"text": "pero ", "start": 10.67, "end": 10.844}, {"text": "es ", "start": 10.879, "end": 10.937}, {"text": "muy ", "start": 11.006, "end": 11.169}, {"text": "linda ", "start": 11.215, "end": 11.564}, {"text": "y ", "start": 11.622, "end": 11.645}, {"text": "cómoda.", "start": 11.726, "end": 13.038}]}, {"id": "p1s5", "text": "Me gusta mucho mi ciudad porque tiene muchos parques.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Me ", "start": 13.63, "end": 13.758}, {"text": "gusta ", "start": 13.781, "end": 14.048}, {"text": "mucho ", "start": 14.095, "end": 14.373}, {"text": "mi ", "start": 14.42, "end": 14.501}, {"text": "ciudad ", "start": 14.524, "end": 14.896}, {"text": "porque ", "start": 14.942, "end": 15.186}, {"text": "tiene ", "start": 15.232, "end": 15.453}, {"text": "muchos ", "start": 15.499, "end": 15.836}, {"text": "parques.", "start": 15.929, "end": 16.765}]}, {"id": "p1s6", "text": "El clima acá es bueno.", "boundaries": [{"text": "El ", "start": 17.365, "end": 17.562}, {"text": "clima ", "start": 17.62, "end": 17.922}, {"text": "acá ", "start": 17.957, "end": 18.178}, {"text": "es ", "start": 18.247, "end": 18.34}, {"text": "bueno.", "start": 18.422, "end": 19.025}]}, {"id": "p1s7", "text": "Hoy el día está soleado y caluroso.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Hoy ", "start": 19.617, "end": 19.884}, {"text": "el ", "start": 19.942, "end": 20.024}, {"text": "día ", "start": 20.105, "end": 20.384}, {"text": "está ", "start": 20.418, "end": 20.639}, {"text": "soleado ", "start": 20.697, "end": 21.173}, {"text": "y ", "start": 21.243, "end": 21.289}, {"text": "caluroso.", "start": 21.359, "end": 22.206}]}]}, {"id": "p2", "sentences": [{"id": "p2s1", "text": "Yo vivo con mi familia.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Yo ", "start": 22.798, "end": 22.949}, {"text": "vivo ", "start": 22.996, "end": 23.193}, {"text": "con ", "start": 23.24, "end": 23.367}, {"text": "mi ", "start": 23.414, "end": 23.483}, {"text": "familia.", "start": 23.542, "end": 24.226}]}, {"id": "p2s2", "text": "Mi mamá se llama Maria y mi papá se llama João.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Mi ", "start": 24.819, "end": 24.946}, {"text": "mamá ", "start": 25.004, "end": 25.237}, {"text": "se ", "start": 25.306, "end": 25.399}, {"text": "llama ", "start": 25.422, "end": 25.655}, {"text": "Maria ", "start": 25.713, "end": 26.049}, {"text": "y ", "start": 26.107, "end": 26.131}, {"text": "mi ", "start": 26.212, "end": 26.305}, {"text": "papá ", "start": 26.363, "end": 26.641}, {"text": "se ", "start": 26.688, "end": 26.781}, {"text": "llama ", "start": 26.804, "end": 27.059}, {"text": "João.", "start": 27.106, "end": 27.617}]}, {"id": "p2s3", "text": "Mi mamá es profesora y mi papá es chofer.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Mi ", "start": 28.209, "end": 28.325}, {"text": "mamá ", "start": 28.383, "end": 28.592}, {"text": "es ", "start": 28.638, "end": 28.708}, {"text": "profesora ", "start": 28.766, "end": 29.393}, {"text": "y ", "start": 29.451, "end": 29.486}, {"text": "mi ", "start": 29.579, "end": 29.683}, {"text": "papá ", "start": 29.741, "end": 30.043}, {"text": "es ", "start": 30.09, "end": 30.182}, {"text": "chofer.", "start": 30.24, "end": 30.891}]}, {"id": "p2s4", "text": "Tengo una hermana menor.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Tengo ", "start": 31.483, "end": 31.75}, {"text": "una ", "start": 31.796, "end": 31.924}, {"text": "hermana ", "start": 31.947, "end": 32.307}, {"text": "menor.", "start": 32.353, "end": 32.911}]}, {"id": "p2s5", "text": "Su nombre es Ana.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Su ", "start": 34.08, "end": 34.254}, {"text": "nombre ", "start": 34.324, "end": 34.591}, {"text": "es", "start": 34.614, "end": 34.719}]}, {"id": "p2s6", "text": "Ana es estudiante.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Ana ", "start": 35.891, "end": 36.123}, {"text": "es", "start": 36.181, "end": 36.263}]}, {"id": "p2s7", "text": "Nosotros tenemos un perro grande.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Nosotros ", "start": 37.876, "end": 38.445}, {"text": "tenemos ", "start": 38.503, "end": 38.84}, {"text": "un ", "start": 38.956, "end": 39.026}, {"text": "perro", "start": 39.084, "end": 39.339}]}, {"id": "p2s8", "text": "El nombre del perro es Rex.", "boundaries": [{"text": "El ", "start": 40.605, "end": 40.779}, {"text": "nombre ", "start": 40.825, "end": 41.058}, {"text": "del ", "start": 41.092, "end": 41.209}, {"text": "perro ", "start": 41.267, "end": 41.51}, {"text": "es", "start": 41.568, "end": 41.65}]}, {"id": "p2s9", "text": "Él es muy feliz, rápido y juguetón.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Él ", "start": 42.857, "end": 43.02}, {"text": "es ", "start": 43.078, "end": 43.171}, {"text": "muy ", "start": 43.298, "end": 43.484}, {"text": "feliz, ", "start": 43.542, "end": 43.925}, {"text": "rápido ", "start": 43.983, "end": 44.355}, {"text": "y", "start": 44.413, "end": 44.448}]}]}, {"id": "p3", "sentences": [{"id": "p3s1", "text": "Todos los días, me despierto a las siete de la mañana.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Todos ", "start": 45.841, "end": 46.178}, {"text": "los ", "start": 46.247, "end": 46.398}, {"text": "días, ", "start": 46.445, "end": 46.793}, {"text": "me ", "start": 46.816, "end": 46.897}, {"text": "despierto ", "start": 46.932, "end": 47.362}, {"text": "a ", "start": 47.408, "end": 47.431}, {"text": "las ", "start": 47.466, "end": 47.606}, {"text": "siete ", "start": 47.64, "end": 47.954}, {"text": "de ", "start": 47.989, "end": 48.035}, {"text": "la", "start": 48.082, "end": 48.14}]}, {"id": "p3s2", "text": "Voy al baño y me lavo la cara.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Su ", "start": 49.405, "end": 49.591}, {"text": "nombre ", "start": 49.649, "end": 49.916}, {"text": "es ", "start": 49.951, "end": 50.055}, {"text": "Ana. ", "start": 50.206, "end": 50.705}, {"text": "Ana ", "start": 51.297, "end": 51.506}, {"text": "es", "start": 51.541, "end": 51.611}]}, {"id": "p3s3", "text": "Tomo café con leche y como pan con manteca.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Nosotros ", "start": 53.201, "end": 53.747}, {"text": "tenemos ", "start": 53.805, "end": 54.095}, {"text": "un ", "start": 54.188, "end": 54.235}, {"text": "perro ", "start": 54.281, "end": 54.49}, {"text": "grande. ", "start": 54.537, "end": 55.175}, {"text": "El", "start": 55.767, "end": 55.93}]}, {"id": "p3s4", "text": "Después, voy al trabajo en colectivo.", "boundaries": [{"text": "nombre ", "start": 55.976, "end": 56.197}, {"text": "del ", "start": 56.232, "end": 56.348}, {"text": "perro ", "start": 56.406, "end": 56.673}, {"text": "es ", "start": 56.731, "end": 56.824}, {"text": "Rex. ", "start": 56.951, "end": 57.451}, {"text": "Él ", "start": 58.043, "end": 58.205}, {"text": "es ", "start": 58.263, "end": 58.333}, {"text": "muy", "start": 58.461, "end": 58.658}]}, {"id": "p3s5", "text": "El viaje es largo.", "boundaries": [{"text": "rápido ", "start": 59.204, "end": 59.587}, {"text": "y", "start": 59.657, "end": 59.703}]}, {"id": "p3s6", "text": "Yo trabajo en una oficina.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Todos ", "start": 61.096, "end": 61.433}, {"text": "los ", "start": 61.503, "end": 61.654}, {"text": "días, ", "start": 61.7, "end": 62.025}, {"text": "me", "start": 62.048, "end": 62.141}]}, {"id": "p3s7", "text": "Mi trabajo empieza a las nueve y termina a las cinco de la tarde.", "boundaries": [{"text": "a ", "start": 62.675, "end": 62.698}, {"text": "las ", "start": 62.733, "end": 62.873}, {"text": "siete ", "start": 62.907, "end": 63.221}, {"text": "de ", "start": 63.256, "end": 63.314}, {"text": "la ", "start": 63.349, "end": 63.407}, {"text": "mañana. ", "start": 63.453, "end": 64.022}, {"text": "empieza ", "start": 65.322, "end": 65.717}, {"text": "a ", "start": 65.752, "end": 65.775}, {"text": "las ", "start": 65.81, "end": 65.949}, {"text": "nueve ", "start": 66.03, "end": 66.321}, {"text": "y ", "start": 66.356, "end": 66.39}, {"text": "termina ", "start": 66.483, "end": 66.82}, {"text": "a", "start": 66.843, "end": 66.866}]}, {"id": "p3s8", "text": "Me gusta mi trabajo.", "boundaries": [{"text": "cinco ", "start": 67.11, "end": 67.412}, {"text": "de ", "start": 67.459, "end": 67.517}, {"text": "la", "start": 67.563, "end": 67.633}]}]}, {"id": "p4", "sentences": [{"id": "p4s1", "text": "En mi tiempo libre, me gusta leer libros y escuchar música.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Me ", "start": 69.394, "end": 69.557}, {"text": "gusta ", "start": 69.591, "end": 69.858}, {"text": "mi ", "start": 69.905, "end": 69.974}, {"text": "trabajo. ", "start": 70.009, "end": 70.718}, {"text": "En ", "start": 71.31, "end": 71.472}, {"text": "mi ", "start": 7