 días.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Yo ", "start": 89.089, "end": 89.251}, {"text": "tomo ", "start": 89.309, "end": 89.576}, {"text": "mucha ", "start": 89.634, "end": 89.959}, {"text": "agua ", "start": 89.994, "end": 90.285}, {"text": "todos ", "start": 90.412, "end": 90.726}, {"text": "los", "start": 90.795, "end": 90.935}]}, {"id": "p4s7", "text": "A la noche, estudio inglés en la computadora por una hora.", "boundaries": [{"text": "A ", "start": 92.177, "end": 92.235}, {"text": "la ", "start": 92.305, "end": 92.374}, {"text": "noche, ", "start": 92.421, "end": 92.816}, {"text": "estudio ", "start": 92.85, "end": 93.245}, {"text": "inglés ", "start": 93.28, "end": 93.535}, {"text": "en ", "start": 93.593, "end": 93.64}, {"text": "la ", "start": 93.675, "end": 93.733}, {"text": "computadora ", "start": 93.768, "end": 94.394}, {"text": "por ", "start": 94.464, "end": 94.603}, {"text": "una", "start": 94.661, "end": 94.778}]}]}, {"id": "p5", "sentences": [{"id": "p5s1", "text": "El fin de semana, yo no trabajo.", "boundaries": [{"text": "El ", "start": 95.846, "end": 96.02}, {"text": "fin ", "start": 96.066, "end": 96.206}, {"text": "de ", "start": 96.24, "end": 96.298}, {"text": "semana, ", "start": 96.344, "end": 96.809}, {"text": "yo ", "start": 96.937, "end": 97.064}, {"text": "no", "start": 97.111, "end": 97.169}]}, {"id": "p5s2", "text": "El sábado a la mañana, voy al parque con mi perro y mi hermana.", "boundaries": [{"text": "El ", "start": 98.516, "end": 98.713}, {"text": "sábado ", "start": 98.794, "end": 99.166}, {"text": "a ", "start": 99.224, "end": 99.247}, {"text": "la ", "start": 99.282, "end": 99.34}, {"text": "mañana, ", "start": 99.375, "end": 99.758}, {"text": "voy ", "start": 99.781, "end": 99.944}, {"text": "al ", "start": 99.978, "end": 100.036}, {"text": "parque ", "start": 100.118, "end": 100.431}, {"text": "con ", "start": 100.489, "end": 100.629}, {"text": "mi ", "start": 100.675, "end": 100.756}, {"text": "perro ", "start": 100.826, "end"